            <title>[HBASE-11357] Expand Hbase Shell Describe Command to list the columns as well of the Column Family</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11357</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the describe command only lists out the column family of a particular table and does not list out the specific columns within that family. It would be good expand the describe command to give a detailed description of the table inclusive of all the columns within that family.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
