                            <comment id="14033250" author="ravishanbhag" created="Tue, 17 Jun 2014 00:33:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Understood Anoop. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I realize that not all columns would be applicable or used by each row but is it not worthwhile to consider displaying a &quot;superset&quot; of columns for each table? &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
